Indian gold closes steady , silver falls . * * Gold 24 carat closed unchanged at 4 , 750 rupees per 10 gramme . * * Gold was down by 40 rupees per 10 gramme during last week as wedding season demand low . * * Prices of a gold biscuit ( 116 . 50 gramme ) closed steady at 55 , 500 rupees per piece after losing 600 rupees last week . * * Silver ( . 999 ) closed 10 rupees lower at 6 , 795 rupees per kg against the previous close of 6 , 805 rupees but up 15 rupees per kg against today ' s opening level of 6 , 780 rupees as early declines drew in industrial buying . - - 
